{"id":"33935627048524ec4de7d32412d3ed3d40d0275a","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1228419","title":"kimi 算力顶不住停售了","site_name":"Info Flow","source":"V2EX (创意工作者社区)","byline":"YanSeven","excerpt":"程序员 - @YanSeven - 所以目前国内市场高端大模型仍然是供不应求？国产卡的能力和产能到底行不行。","content_html":"<DIV class=\"page\" id=\"readability-page-1\"><div id=\"Main\">\n                \n                \n<div>\n    \n    <div><p><a href=\"/member/YanSeven\"><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3f22/feff/383743_xlarge.png?m=1778835129\" width=\"73\" alt=\"YanSeven\" data-uid=\"383743\"></a></p>\n    \n    \n    \n     &#160; <p><small><a href=\"/member/YanSeven\">YanSeven</a> · <span title=\"2026-07-20 00:23:07 +08:00\">22h 25m ago</span> via Android · 3730 views</small>\n    </p></div>\n    \n    \n    \n    <div><p>所以目前国内市场高端大模型仍然是供不应求？</p>\n<p>国产卡的能力和产能到底行不行。</p>\n</div>\n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \n</div>\n\n<!-- SOL tip topic -->\n\n\n\n\n\n<div>\n    <div><P><a href=\"/tag/算力\"><li></li> 算力</a><a href=\"/tag/大模型\"><li></li> 大模型</a><a href=\"/tag/供需\"><li></li> 供需</a></P><p><span>15 replies &#160;<strong>•</strong> &#160;2026-07-20 20:06:16 +08:00</span>\n    </p></div>\n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17881451\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e983/e553/821265_normal.png?m=1784448292\" alt=\"larongryan\" data-uid=\"821265\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>1</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/larongryan\">larongryan</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-20 00:31:06 +08:00\">22h 17m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>新建算力中心和完成进度低于 30%的算力中心，禁用英伟达，切 80%绿点。这条条框框卡的紧很。而且各省的超算中心不知道建给谁用的，看不懂。电信 3 巨头的 token 价格简直是在宰猪。</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17881459\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a999/2f6c/19458_normal.png?m=1743308829\" alt=\"cskeleton\" data-uid=\"19458\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>2</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/cskeleton\">cskeleton</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-20 00:38:10 +08:00\">22h 10m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <div><p>然后上了新的套餐了，当然也不能买。</p><p>然后确实算力很不够。刚出来一两天，我直接调 API 都会提示负载过高不让用。</p></div>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17881491\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2dc4dfe787daf095c067e4c3a76b6192?s=48&d=retro\" alt=\"stephen123456cn\" data-uid=\"603261\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>3</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/stephen123456cn\">stephen123456cn</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-20 01:06:51 +08:00\">21h 41m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>不是停售吧，感觉是上新会员计划停机维护，虽然 Coding Plan 的价格很抽象，1M 上下文还要高一级的订阅-_-||</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17881510\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/17d3/d5c9/71891_normal.png?m=1752241801\" alt=\"106npo\" data-uid=\"71891\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>5</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/106npo\">106npo</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-20 01:29:04 +08:00\">21h 19m ago via Android</span> \n                    \n                    <p>先全部停售，然后立马上新套餐，但所有人只能看不能买 😂这哪像停售啊，就其实是新套餐收集下舆论反应。</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17881931\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c0a2/b1b1/462556_normal.png?m=1710309608\" alt=\"AmiKara\" data-uid=\"462556\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>8</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/AmiKara\">AmiKara</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-20 09:38:57 +08:00\">13h 9m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>看 kimi 和 glm 的操作就知道，国内算力还远远不够，加上以后大家都是大参数模型，算力需求只会越来越多</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17882450\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/eed5/484b/152333_normal.png?m=1769061596\" alt=\"rb6221\" data-uid=\"152333\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>9</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/rb6221\">rb6221</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-20 10:48:54 +08:00\">11h 59m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>暂停是暂停，也没说啥时候恢复啊，这种也可以理解为商业层面的话术，甚至可以怀疑是故意为之：<br>先定个高价，而且故意把 99 档的性价比做的很低，让大家都去买 199+<br>然后触发卡顿，真实性先信任一波是真的吧<br>再宣布暂停 coding plan ，同时趁机调整权益<br>再后面端出来的就是 token plan 甚至按量付费了</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17882562\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2dc4dfe787daf095c067e4c3a76b6192?s=48&d=retro\" alt=\"stephen123456cn\" data-uid=\"603261\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>10</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/stephen123456cn\">stephen123456cn</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-20 11:06:36 +08:00\">11h 42m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>凌晨时分看到上新了会员体系（定价抽象，99 元起，定价断层，第二档 299 元及以上才可以用 K3 1M 上下文），今早再看已经恢复了，而且可以续费和新订阅，不知道在搞啥子</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17882704\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/4915301cf6d5cf66ce795eac331f5f28?s=48&d=retro\" alt=\"ziyeziye\" data-uid=\"341568\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>11</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/ziyeziye\">ziyeziye</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-20 11:21:37 +08:00\">11h 27m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>还可以买, k2.5 出来的时候,开过周卡体验, 应该是被标记为老用户了. 刚刚开了 1 个月的 199 套餐</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17882912\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f8158ec628551d3f66620d3d0c38c776?s=48&d=retro\" alt=\"kingba\" data-uid=\"236742\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>12</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/kingba\">kingba</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-20 11:50:40 +08:00\">10h 58m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>先速度订阅了，免得出什么幺蛾子</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17884242\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/edca324d47716a2926b39c2c75184adb?s=48&d=retro\" alt=\"526457385\" data-uid=\"648590\"></td>\n  